  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink124">
<l>kaṇṭiku mallamō koṇkaniṉ kēḷē</l>
<l>vaṇṭaṟ pāvai vauvali</l>
<l>ṉuṇpoṭi yaḷaiik kaṭaṟūrp pōḷē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We have seen your friend, haven't we, oh man from the maritime tract?</l>
<l>She who filled up the ocean, having mixed together fine powders,</l>
<l>Due to the snatching [by the ocean] of her play-doll?</l>
</lg>
    </div>
